{"tid":1038271,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)鬼船 特務型戰 猛火爆","createTime":"2019-02-26T14:23:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-26T22:02:38.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"cd55b92bcba41133fb2097e4b7566db1b2b67720","tid":1038271,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T14:23:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=zkxYWYOkbsQg7WdKzXEy6bvH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=0cfebaac\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> 關左ADBLOCK可以睇到V台好似係<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=zkxYWYOkbsQg7WdKzXEy6bvH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=9ac1f735\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a>可以直接睇到V台 *暫時無左OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=zkxYWYOkbsQg7WdKzXEy6bvH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=f7faeca8\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/5/55/Ghost_Ship_poster.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2F5%2F55%2FGhost_Ship_poster.JPG&h=f86217e6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/0/01/The_Man_from_U.N.C.L.E._Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F0%2F01%2FThe_Man_from_U.N.C.L.E._Poster.jpg&h=221fe847&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/c/c4/%E7%8C%9B%E7%81%AB%E7%88%86.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fc%2Fc4%2F%25E7%258C%259B%25E7%2581%25AB%25E7%2588%2586.jpg&h=946b05f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.安東妮雅葛莎號，是1954年在熱拿亞船塢建造的巨型遊輪，裝潢設備卻極盡奢華，被喻為人類史上第一座海上皇宮。這艘海上宮殿的保險由倫敦的羅氏保險公司所承保，並於1962年5月21日在拉布拉多半島海岸外失蹤。 非常奇怪的是，它並沒有發出求救信號或跟任何船隻通話，它就這樣憑空消失得無影無蹤。從那一天起，世上每一名打撈船長以及每一位乘客的親人都在尋找它，希望『安東妮雅葛莎號』並沒有沉船。 四十年的時間很快過去，『安東妮雅葛莎號』失蹤疑雲也在人們的記憶中漸漸變得模糊...<br />\n<br />\n2.故事背景定於1960年代的冷戰時期，美國中央情報局（CIA）特務拿破崙&middot;蘇洛（亨利&middot;卡維爾飾）和蘇聯國安局（KGB）特務伊利亞&middot;科里亞金（艾米&middot;漢默飾）被迫合作，阻止一個神秘的國際犯罪組織 「T.H.R.U.S.H.[註 1]」，原來這個組織是納粹餘黨，他們綁架了一名核武專家泰勒博士（克里斯丁&middot;伯克飾），意圖引爆第三次世界大戰，蘇洛與科里亞金找到了專家住在東柏林的愛女蓋比&middot;泰勒（艾莉西亞&middot;薇坎德飾），偕往羅馬尋找泰勒博士，將核彈沒收，以阻止核災的發生；但其實蓋比早被英國軍情六處（MI6）招募..<br />\n<br />\n3.法蘭克莫西斯（Frank Moses；布魯斯&middot;威利飾演）是一名自CIA退休的前特工，被CIA的分類為RED，即為已退休而極度危險的（Retired, Extremely Dangerous），他感到退休生活十分無趣沒有變化，唯一的樂趣是每月撕毀養老金支票藉故與養老金管理人莎拉羅斯（Sarah Ross；瑪莉&middot;露易絲&middot;派克飾演）在電話裡的談天說地時間，且法蘭克對莎拉在心中漸生情愫；一日法蘭克家中突然闖入了數名傭兵，想要將法蘭克滅口，法蘭克憑著過去的矯健身手將傭兵團擊退後，發現攻擊的背後有著巨大的陰謀存在；因此為了保護所愛的人，法蘭克決定召集過去的老戰友們，來對抗陰謀的幕後黑手並揭發真相&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n11 00PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=zkxYWYOkbsQg7WdKzXEy6bvH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=e92ff7a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=zkxYWYOkbsQg7WdKzXEy6bvH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=5f168d1d\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04e55983d96fec4851de0b26738f9354f0882fc1","tid":1038271,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T14:46:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c68235783627a570e35b97d4b5f8a7531643441","tid":1038271,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T15:02:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71670869f3e49a2408d96335d59b2b0cec7129bf","tid":1038271,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T16:04:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"599c1875a71010b6bf45e2c7e6596c7c255b1487","tid":1038271,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T17:35:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7d5d022768a45ff7cc568cd0bf27b827e281765","tid":1038271,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T17:55:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc70c47d68eeef89b3873fd7db2e95d49d398d5e","tid":1038271,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T20:56:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1d3ba0afaaafd599df42976971ca5bf905421aa","